The Life of Pablo Listening Party
Yeezy Season 3 show at Madison Square Garden
introduction: The Life Of Pablo is Kanye West's seventh studio album, which was released on February 14, 2016 by GOOD Music, Roc-A-Fella Records, and Def Jam. The album premiered at Madison Square Garden on February 11, 2016 as part of his "Yeezy Season 3" fashion show, in collaboration with Adidas.
